\v 5 \wj \+w No|strong="H3808"\+w* busquen \+w a|strong="H3068"\+w* Bet-ʼEl, \+w ni|strong="H3808"\+w* vayan \+w a|strong="H3068"\+w* \+w Gilgal|strong="H1537"\+w*, \+w ni|strong="H3808"\+w* pasen \+w a|strong="H3068"\+w* Beerseba, \+w porque|strong="H3588"\+w* \+w Gilgal|strong="H1537"\+w* \+w ciertamente|strong="H3588"\+w* irá \+w en|strong="H3588"\+w* cautiverio \+w y|strong="H3588"\+w* Bet-ʼEl \+w será|strong="H1961"\+w* reducida \+w a|strong="H3068"\+w* escombro.\wj*   
